      "id": "PopularPost315814",
      "post_content": "I don't think some of you guys get how this card works in practice.  \n  \nFirst, you play Dystopia. Your opponent has to sacrifice a green or white permanent on their turn. On your turn, you pay 1 life, if you want. Then your opponent sacrifices a second permanent on his turn. Then, if you want to keep it around, you pay 2 life, then your opponent sacrifices a THIRD permanent. For 3 life you've made him sacrifice 3 permanents, and you can stop there if you want or pay 4 life after that to make him sacrifice a fourth.  \n  \nThis is crushing from one card.",
      "posted_by": "EGarrett01",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost315814\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">I don't think some of you guys get how this card works in practice.<br/><br/>First, you play Dystopia. Your opponent has to sacrifice a green or white permanent on their turn. On your turn, you pay 1 life, if you want. Then your opponent sacrifices a second permanent on his turn. Then, if you want to keep it around, you pay 2 life, then your opponent sacrifices a THIRD permanent. For 3 life you've made him sacrifice 3 permanents, and you can stop there if you want or pay 4 life after that to make him sacrifice a fourth.<br/><br/>This is crushing from one card.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '315814'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy31635\">EGarrett01</span>\r\n                                (5/13/2013 3:52:22 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.pn