      "id": "PopularPost309830",
      "post_content": "For 0-3 life you'll hit 1-3 permanents; which is great. This is a beast in legacy; hitting at least half of the big power creatures:  \n-[progenitus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=progenitus) (natural order)  \n-[tarmogoyf](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=tarmogoyf) (almost every deck)  \n-[knight of the reliquary](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=knight of the reliquary) (maverick + other decks)  \n-[qasali pridemage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=qasali pridemage) (maverick + others)  \n-[deathrite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=deathrite) (almost every deck)  \n-[nimble mongoose](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=nimble mongoose) (RUG delver, tempo/threshold green)  \n-[mother of runes](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mother of runes) (death and taxes. It actually hits the entire deck.)  \n  \nIn other words, it hits many many power-creatures in legacy. If you run any kind of black control, this is worth considering as it'll screw entire decks if given a turn or 3.  \n  \nIn W/B legacy this is tutorable with [Enlightened Tutor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Enlightened Tutor) and is recurrable with [Sun Titan](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sun Titan).",
      "posted_by": "blurrymadness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost309830\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">For 0-3 life you'll hit 1-3 permanents; which is great. This is a beast in legacy; hitting at least half of the big power creatures:<br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"progenitus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=progenitus\">progenitus</a> (natural order)<br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"tarmogoyf\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=tarmogoyf\">tarmogoyf</a> (almost every deck)<br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"knight of the reliquary\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=knight of the reliquary\">knight of the reliquary</a> (maverick + other decks)<br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"qasali pridemage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=qasali pridemage\">qasali pridemage</a> (maverick + others)<br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"deathrite\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=deathrite\">deathrite</a> (almost every deck)<br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"nimble mongoose\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=nimble mongoose\">nimble mongoose</a> (RUG delver, tempo/threshold green)<br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"mother of runes\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mother of runes\">mother of runes</a> (death and taxes. It actually hits the entire deck.)<br/><br/>In other words, it hits many many power-creatures in legacy. If you run any kind of black control, this is worth considering as it'll screw entire decks if given a turn or 3.<br/><br/>In W/B legacy this is tutorable with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Enlightened Tutor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Enlightened Tutor\">Enlightened Tutor</a> and is recurrable with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sun Titan\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sun Titan\">Sun Titan</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '309830'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44651\">blurrymadness</span>\r\n                                (8/23/2013 12:31:26 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"floa