      "id": "PopularPost100072",
      "post_content": "You. Don't. Have. To. Pay. The. Upkeep. Therefor, absurdly good. This is the -only- black card you will see dealing with your opponent's [Moat](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Moat) with Shroud. Enough said? Combine this with [Perish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Perish). But this can also hit white... so against zoo you can get them to sacrifice 2 or 3 creatures like [Knight Of The Reliquary](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Knight Of The Reliquary)",
